{"tid":2445790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獸印 precursor 竟然係以色列開始","createTime":"2021-03-14T02:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T14:25:47.000Z","uid":222614,"like":64,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"34d301a90cecc8196cf73e774506fbf7300efd28","tid":2445790,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"猶太人抗議 Netanyahu 嘅 &quot;Green Pass&quot; programme<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=POS6ftKhDAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPOS6ftKhDAs&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=a2f11dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=POS6ftKhDAs</a><br />\n<br />\n以色列嘅 Green Pass 類似香港嘅「健康碼」，被視為另一個層次嘅公民身份<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WMsn0bj_P6o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWMsn0bj_P6o&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=dbf68694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WMsn0bj_P6o</a><br />\n<br />\n當然呢個肯定唔係啓示錄所講嘅獸印，因為 Jacob's Trouble 仲未開始<br />\n但有啲獸印嘅特質，例如無佢就唔可以進行某啲日常活動<br />\n<br />\n啓示錄記載，敵基督會要求所有人接受獸印，否則不可進行買賣<br />\n&quot;And that no man might buy or sell, save he that had the mark, or the name of the beast, or the number of his name.&quot; Revelation 13:17<br />\n<br />\n猶太人擔心，無 Green Pass 就唔可以舉行聚會，買機票，進入公眾場所等等<br />\n係對人權嘅嚴重踐踏"},{"pid":"467a2a7aa76884f957bd3fa99e7bc08dcf519230","tid":2445790,"uid":222614,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"Green Pass = The Mark for a healthy, law biding, tax paying citizen"},{"pid":"5eded6191bc9b6e4413c59623f9d907f44ceeb04","tid":2445790,"uid":91397,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"大淫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9722e04fa0fca8dbd02e58f9ea6cdccad94fd422","tid":2445790,"uid":222614,"li