印，否則不可進行買賣<br />\n&quot;And that no man might buy or sell, save he that had the mark, or the name of the beast, or the number of his name.&quot; Revelation 13:17<br />\n<br />\n猶太人擔心，無 Green Pass 就唔可以舉行聚會，買機票，進入公眾場所等等<br />\n係對人權嘅嚴重踐踏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"我始終認為佢會係中俄聯盟底下出現<br />\n<br />\n佢地玩左膠思想<br />\n<br />\n人人都會覺得裝左係大勢所趨<br />\n<br />\n而只有中俄聯盟係最有機會成就跨國身分認證系統"},{"pid":"10e8688137b94a25165f2bb2005f8e3574a76995","tid":2445790,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:58:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"43e20e3e2e4d3ae0c374a5c5cd7e322a10a78d8d","tid":2445790,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"咁猶太人下次係咪要比自己人屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff72d7190631064223dfdfdadef03a7d92749681","tid":2445790,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:02:17.000Z","msg":"樓主是對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73f9b7280f5bfb47ebc501aeb6bb2c94aeeab6c","tid":2445790,"uid":129138,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084abe46970b2cbfddf783ce3d8e56ea95427bd2","tid":2445790,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"614e23e7da9a59c449ff137c595168eb6c935b2f","tid":2445790,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"583ec08c6458d33e685a6604ae153e3588928e40","tid":2445790,"uid":267494,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:50:23.000Z","msg":"咁講法21世紀最大獸印係中共<br />\n唔支持佢同配合佢就無得做佢生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:56:55.000Z","msg":"中共=聖經入面一條火紅色的巨龍，有七個頭和十隻角，七個頭上戴著七個王冠。"},{"pid":"d133268bfba25f8f2aa023bb32316a9d05ace0f7","